cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.SY 

The paper discusses a practical method for federated learning of deep networks, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also deals with communication efficiency, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper uses datasets, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper also deals with image models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
